<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Welcome to Coatcard AI</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
    <style>body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; }</style>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
</head>
<body class="bg-yellow-50 flex items-center justify-center h-screen">
    <div class="text-center p-8 max-w-2xl">
        <div class="mb-8">
            <h1 class="text-6xl font-bold text-yellow-900">Coatcard AI</h1>
            <p class="text-xl text-amber-700 mt-2">Your Personal Coding Assistant</p>
        </div>
        <div class="space-x-4 mb-8">
            <a href="/login" class="px-8 py-3 bg-yellow-400 text-stone-800 font-semibold rounded-lg shadow-md hover:bg-yellow-500 transition-transform transform hover:scale-105">
                Login
            </a>
            <a href="/register" class="px-8 py-3 bg-white text-yellow-800 font-semibold rounded-lg shadow-md hover:bg-gray-100 transition-transform transform hover:scale-105">
                Register
            </a>
        </div>
        
        <!-- New Section: Why Use Me -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-6 border border-yellow-200 text-left">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-yellow-800 mb-4">I am Coatcard AI</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">An expert AI assistant designed to help you with computer science and programming topics.</p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-800">
                <li><strong>Expertise:</strong> I specialize in providing clear, concise, and accurate information, particularly in <span class="text-blue-700 font-medium">C++</span>.</li>
                <li><strong>Structured Learning:</strong> I break down complex topics into digestible sections, including logic, code, and explanations.</li>
                <li><strong>Optimization:</strong> I provide both brute-force and optimized solutions to coding problems, helping you understand the trade-offs.</li>
                <li><strong>Exam Preparation:</strong> I can switch to <span class="text-red-600 font-semibold">"Exam Time"</span> mode to provide clean, optimized code for practice.</li>
                <li><strong>Focused Assistance:</strong> I tailor responses based on your role, field, and goals, ensuring the information is relevant and useful to you.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
